sentences: KMC (born 5 January 1971) is a soca artist from Trinidad.
Considered to be one of Trinidad's top soca artists, KMC has over sixteen years experience in the music industry.
In 1998, he decided to test his skills in the Soca genre, bursting onto the scene with songs like "Kaya", "Bashment to Carnival" and "Soca Bashment".
In April 2005, KMC was signed to the American music label Sequence Records.

In October 2005, KMC joined Beenie Man on his US "King of the Dancehall" tour.
